Basci Says Turkey, China Discussing Local Currency Swaps

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y   a n d   S e l c u k   G o k o l u k
-- 
2011-09-28T11:56:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/basci-says-turkey-china-discussing-local-currency-swaps.html
Turkey and  China  are holding
“advanced” talks on currency swaps that would enable the two
countries to trade in their local currencies, Turkish central
bank governor Erdem Basci said in Istanbul today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
